&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=iamaleksey&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;iamaleksey&quot;&gt;iamaleksey&lt;/a&gt;, this looks like an oversight from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-9673&quot; title=&quot;Improve batchlog write path&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-9673&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-9673&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, so I am assigning you as a reviewer in case your memory is better than mine and can recall a reason why we wanted to move it to the end.&lt;/p&gt;

